WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.140 --> 00:00:05.700
Have you had trouble finding shoes that you
love, if you're a size 10 or larger?

00:00:05.700 --> 00:00:10.550
I want to connect with you.

00:00:10.550 --> 00:00:21.359
Hi, I'm Isabel Prosper, and I wear a size
10.

00:00:21.359 --> 00:00:26.480
I'm the creator of and founder behind, prettylongfeet.com,
and I want to share with you my story today.

00:00:26.480 --> 00:00:30.569
There were lots of times growing up, when
I was searching for shoes, and I couldn't

00:00:30.569 --> 00:00:35.120
find the shoes that I wanted, so, we often
went down to the States as a family, and I've

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:37.440
ordered online, and I've had good experiences.

00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:42.890
But when the shoes arrived, I'd hate to pay
the Customs fees.

00:00:42.890 --> 00:00:48.910
So, I wanted to create a community, where
I can make it easier for women like us, to

00:00:48.910 --> 00:00:53.420
find shoes, right here, being in Canada, I
wanted to solve the problem: let's be able

00:00:53.420 --> 00:00:56.960
to find shoes online, today, right here, right
now.

00:00:56.960 --> 00:01:02.269
Whether it's for your style, or your fashion
look, or it's a functional look that you're

00:01:02.269 --> 00:01:03.320
trying to complete.

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:08.600
This is about more than just selling shoes
on a website: this is about creating a community.

00:01:08.600 --> 00:01:14.420
I want to create a community of women, where
we can empower each other, by sharing our

00:01:14.420 --> 00:01:19.460
stories, our struggles, our experiences, and
sometimes, those stories will be funny, and

00:01:19.460 --> 00:01:24.290
I welcome all of that, through that, we can
build each others' confidence.

00:01:24.290 --> 00:01:29.400
At the same time, I want to share with you
that this company believes in being compassionate,

00:01:29.400 --> 00:01:32.030
being humble, and believe in giving.

00:01:32.030 --> 00:01:36.420
This is our mission: so, through this, we
are going to empower girls all over the world.

00:01:36.420 --> 00:01:38.479
And you're going to be part of this.

00:01:38.479 --> 00:01:42.439
We will do that by giving with the profits
from the company.

00:01:42.439 --> 00:01:47.650
So you can join us to share your story, become
part of this community, today, no matter where

00:01:47.650 --> 00:01:48.650
you are, actually.

00:01:48.650 --> 00:01:52.400
If you're watching this video, and you're
in Ireland, please join us.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:53.649
And share your story.

00:01:53.649 --> 00:01:59.719
You can find us on Facebook, Pretty Long Feet;
you can also find us on Twitter, and we have

00:01:59.719 --> 00:02:00.719
a blog.

00:02:00.719 --> 00:02:03.930
You can follow our blog at prettylongfeet.wordpress.com.

00:02:03.930 --> 00:02:20.859
Thank you so much, I look forward to hearing
from you.

